---
title: Quick Indian Mango Chicken & Garlicky Veggies with Rapid Rice & Yoghurt
description: Bold Mumbai spice blend coats diced chicken in this quick and easy Indian-inspired dish! With a bit of help from the yoghurt and
mango chutney toppings, the aromas will make you want to dig in before this hits the table.

